Author: Whoimi
Title: [ANN][ICO] 🔥🔥 VendiCoins: The Next Generation Video Advertising Platform 🔥🔥
Body: Vendio's video interactive platform (VIP) combines the communication gap between the content of the publisher, the interest of the viewers and the advertiser.  Vendio implements its own tagging algorithm, added to a fragment of video content at a specific time during a certain duration of the video selected by the publisher. These tags accurately describe the visual content displayed during the selected time. The data in the tags and asset information is then passed on to potential advertisers to select the publisher, which then selects the best ad that corresponds to the specific content labeled by the publisher.

The Video Interactive Platform (VIP) utilizes VendiCoins – VENDI tokens to feed all in-app and on-site transactional processes. VENDI tokens are at the epicenter of the Platform. No payment or transaction can be conducted without VENDI, which is regulated by smart-contracts. VENDI tokens are used by and directly benefit all parties involved. Vendio’s future plans involve listing its tokens on cryptocurrency exchanges to enlarge its userbase and fulfill users’ expectations to provide the most comprehensive services via The Video Interactive Platform (VIP). VendiCoins are purpose-built Coins using the Vendio platform that will allow members to use engage in all in-app functions. VendiCoins are utilities tokens which give rights and privileges to their owners when using the Vendio platform and its services. VendiCoins are not securities. Author: elaky
Title: [ANN][ICO] 🔥🔥 VendiCoins: The Next Generation Video Advertising Platform 🔥🔥
Body: The Video Interactive Platform (VIP) bridges the communication gap between publisher content, viewer interest and the advertiser by connecting relevant ads to the publisher’s media being consumed by the viewer. The method used to do so is what differentiates Vendio from any other advertising instrument currently available today.  1 The publisher selects specifically isolated portions of the video clip that they would like to make available for an ad placement relevant to what is on screen 2 To ensure the advertisement’s precise relevancy to the clip, the publisher adds several niche tags that accurately describe the selected video clip 3 Here the publisher adds basic asset information and sets their desired price 4 In the Asset Description section the publisher provides a detailed description of what is happening on screen to help advertisers connect the most relevant ads 5 The Gas Price is how many VendiCoins (VENDI) it will cost to make their video content available to advertisers. The cost in always nominal 6 VendiMatch™ is a proprietary algorithm that matches the best paying advertisers, having the most relevant ads, to the publisher’s selected clips click to enlarge image  Vendio implements a proprietary tagging algorithm appended to a piece of video content at specific times during a specific video duration, selected by the publisher. These tags accurately describe the visual content being displayed during the specific duration of time selected. The data within the tags and asset information is then shared with potential advertisers of the publisher’s choice, who then select the best advertisement to match the specific content tagged by the publisher.  Vendio’s analytics provide in-depth data for both the publisher and advertiser via the platform dashboard. Every publisher and advertiser are also given a VENDI Score used to gauge how successful each publisher and advertiser is in relation to their content.  1,000,000 Minutes of video watched /second by 2021 $17,000,000,000 Spent on video advertising via social media by 2021 100,000,000 Hours of video watched on Facebook daily  Vendio’s future plans involve listing its tokens on cryptocurrency exchanges to enlarge its userbase and fulfill users’ expectations to provide the most comprehensive services via The Video Interactive Platform (VIP).  Anticipated Listings  The Video Interactive Platform (VIP) utilizes VendiCoins – VENDI tokens to feed all in-app and on-site transactional processes. VENDI tokens are at the epicenter of the Platform. No payment or transaction can be conducted without VENDI, which is regulated by smart-contracts. VENDI tokens are used by and directly benefit all parties involved. & more Vendio passes the Howey Test provided by the POA Network team based on the framework by New York, NY based law firm Debevoise & Plimpton LLP, published on Coindesk.  VendiCoins are purpose-built Coins using the Vendio platform that will allow members to use engage in all in-app functions. VendiCoins are utilities tokens which give rights and privileges to their owners when using the Vendio platform and its services. VendiCoins are not securities. VendiCoins are available at a discount during the ICO & Pre-ICO events. Any unsold coins during the ICO will be burned.

Title: [ANN][ICO] 🔥🔥 VendiCoins: The Next Generation Video Advertising Platform 🔥🔥
Body: Quote from: VendiCoins on February 10, 2018, 12:21:30 AM VendiCoins World’s First Crypto Advertising Platform & Token Whitepaper|Website|Telegram|Facebook|Twitter|Youtube|Reddit  http://vendicoins.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/bitcointalk-header.jpg  Vendio's Video Interactive Platform (VIP) bridges the communication gap between publisher content, viewer interest and the advertiser by seamlessly connecting relevant ads to the publisher’s media being consumed by the viewer.   Vendio’s future plans involve listing its tokens on cryptocurrency exchanges to enlarge its userbase and fulfill users’ expectations to provide the most comprehensive services via The Video Interactive Platform (VIP). The Video Interactive Platform (VIP) utilizes VendiCoins – VENDI tokens to feed all in-app and on-site transactional processes. VENDI tokens are at the epicenter of the Platform. No payment or transaction can be conducted without VENDI, which is regulated by smart-contracts. VENDI tokens are used by and directly benefit all parties involved. Vendio’s future plans involve listing its tokens on cryptocurrency exchanges to enlarge its userbase and fulfill users’ expectations to provide the most comprehensive services via The Video Interactive Platform (VIP). VendiCoins are purpose-built Coins using the Vendio platform that will allow members to use engage in all in-app functions. VendiCoins are utilities tokens which give rights and privileges to their owners when using the Vendio platform and its services. VendiCoins are not securities. VendiCoins are available at a discount during the ICO & Pre-ICO events.  Any unsold coins during the ICO will be burned.  Distribution of VENDI Tokens  60% Total ICO distribution to the community 15% Tokens allocated for marketing and operations purposes 10% Reserved for the founders and management of the ICO 10% Reserved for team 5% Reserved for ICO partner advisers *ALL TOKENS DISTRIBUTED BY APRIL 1ST, 2018  Presale Bonus Round 1 – 68% Bonus – 500,000 VENDI @ .0005 ETH ($.40) Round 2 – 60% Bonus – 600,000 VENDI @ .0006 ETH ($.50) Round 3 – 48% Bonus – 900,000 VENDI @ .0008 ETH ($.65) ICO Bonus Round 4 – 35% Bonus  – 1,200,000 VENDI @ .001 ETH ($.80) Round 5 – 25% Bonus – 900,000 VENDI @ .00115 ETH ($95) Round 6 – 12% Bonus – 800,000 VENDI @ .00134 ETH ($1.10) Round 7 – Final Round – 600,000 VENDI  Crowdsale Address: 0xfd38567eA6F0E35090cDAabbfd0701d77C7E5A5a  https://i.imgur.com/9N4XCrg.png  https://i.imgur.com/JQjC6DV.png  Moderators: @Vendicoins & @Azaid18

Author: gautam_khairnar
Title: [ANN][ICO] 🔥🔥 VendiCoins: The Next Generation Video Advertising Platform 🔥🔥
Body: Quote from: VendiCoins on February 10, 2018, 12:21:30 AM VendiCoins World’s First Crypto Advertising Platform & Token Whitepaper|Website|Telegram|Facebook|Twitter|Youtube|Reddit  http://vendicoins.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/bitcointalk-header.jpg  Vendio's Video Interactive Platform (VIP) bridges the communication gap between publisher content, viewer interest and the advertiser by seamlessly connecting relevant ads to the publisher’s media being consumed by the viewer.   Vendio’s future plans involve listing its tokens on cryptocurrency exchanges to enlarge its userbase and fulfill users’ expectations to provide the most comprehensive services via The Video Interactive Platform (VIP). The Video Interactive Platform (VIP) utilizes VendiCoins – VENDI tokens to feed all in-app and on-site transactional processes. VENDI tokens are at the epicenter of the Platform. No payment or transaction can be conducted without VENDI, which is regulated by smart-contracts. VENDI tokens are used by and directly benefit all parties involved. Vendio’s future plans involve listing its tokens on cryptocurrency exchanges to enlarge its userbase and fulfill users’ expectations to provide the most comprehensive services via The Video Interactive Platform (VIP). VendiCoins are purpose-built Coins using the Vendio platform that will allow members to use engage in all in-app functions. VendiCoins are utilities tokens which give rights and privileges to their owners when using the Vendio platform and its services. VendiCoins are not securities. VendiCoins are available at a discount during the ICO & Pre-ICO events.  Any unsold coins during the ICO will be burned.  Distribution of VENDI Tokens  60% Total ICO distribution to the community 15% Tokens allocated for marketing and operations purposes 10% Reserved for the founders and management of the ICO 10% Reserved for team 5% Reserved for ICO partner advisers *ALL TOKENS DISTRIBUTED BY APRIL 1ST, 2018  Presale Bonus Round 1 – 68% Bonus – 500,000 VENDI @ .0005 ETH ($.40) Round 2 – 60% Bonus – 600,000 VENDI @ .0006 ETH ($.50) Round 3 – 48% Bonus – 900,000 VENDI @ .0008 ETH ($.65) ICO Bonus Round 4 – 35% Bonus  – 1,200,000 VENDI @ .001 ETH ($.80) Round 5 – 25% Bonus – 900,000 VENDI @ .00115 ETH ($95) Round 6 – 12% Bonus – 800,000 VENDI @ .00134 ETH ($1.10) Round 7 – Final Round – 600,000 VENDI  Crowdsale Address: 0xfd38567eA6F0E35090cDAabbfd0701d77C7E5A5a  https://i.imgur.com/9N4XCrg.png  https://i.imgur.com/JQjC6DV.png  Moderators: @Vendicoins & @Azaid18

Author: VendiCoins
Title: [ANN][ICO] 🔥🔥 VendiCoins: The Next Generation Video Advertising Platform 🔥🔥
Body: Hi there, GREAT question actually! THETA seems to be focused more around infrastructure and easy of video distributions. A great model. However, Vendio's model is much different. We are focused more on video advertising.  Vendio implements a proprietary tagging algorithm appended to a piece of video content at specific times during a specific video duration, selected by the publisher. These tags accurately describe the visual content being displayed during the specific duration of time selected. The data within the tags and asset information is then shared with potential advertisers of the publisher’s choice, who then select the best advertisement to match the specific content tagged by the publisher.  The Vendio Platform will be similar to youtube with better benefits for publishers, views and advertisers alike because; -- Advertisements are more relevant = Better target marketing for the Advertiser -- Better clicks because the advertisements makes sense = More money for the publisher -- Better user experience for the viewer because the ads are specific to what their watching in real time  All around, this is a better video platform for viewing, advertising and publishing. All videos can be shared to any website or social media just like Youtube videos are able to be shared.  I hope this info helps!

Author: VendiCoins
Title: [ANN][ICO] 🔥🔥 VendiCoins: The Next Generation Video Advertising Platform 🔥🔥
Body: VendiCoins Tokens Token Sale World’s First Crypto Advertising Platform & Token Whitepaper|Website|Telegram|Facebook|Twitter|Youtube    Vendio's Video Interactive Platform (VIP) is a next-generation video advertising platform based on artificial intelligence connecting ads specifically targeted to match what is being viewed on-screen. It bridges the communication gap between publisher content, viewer interest and the advertiser by seamlessly connecting relevant ads to the publisher’s media being consumed by the viewer.   The Video Interactive Platform (VIP) utilizes VendiCoins – VENDI tokens to feed all in-app and on-site transactional processes. VENDI tokens are at the epicenter of the Video Interactive Platform (VIP) as they serve to feed the gas used to drive the platform functions among other features. VENDI tokens are used by and directly benefit all parties involved. The Video Interactive Platform (VIP) utilizes VendiCoins – VENDI tokens to feed all in-app and on-site transactional processes. VENDI tokens are at the epicenter of the Platform. No payment or transaction can be conducted without VENDI, which is regulated by smart-contracts. VENDI tokens are used by and directly benefit all parties involved.  VendiCoins are purpose-built Coins using the Vendio platform that will allow members to use engage in all in-app functions. VendiCoins are utilities tokens which give rights and privileges to their owners when using the Vendio platform and its services. VendiCoins are not securities. VendiCoins are available at a discount during the ICO & Pre-ICO events.  Any unsold coins during the ICO will be burned.  Distribution of VENDI Tokens  60% total distribution to the Community 20% will be rewarded to the Partners 10% will be allocated for Development 10% will be rewarded to the Team ALL FUNDS HELD IN ESCROW. KYC COMPLIANT  Presale Bonus Round 1 – 25% Bonus –  ($.20)  –  September 15, 2018 Round 2 – 15% Bonus –  ($.20)  –  September 25, 2018 Round 3 – 10% Bonus –  ($.20)  –  October 3, 2018 ICO Bonus Round 4 – 5% Bonus  – ($.20) –  October 8, 2018 Round 5 – 2.5% Bonus – ($.20) –  October 10, 2018 Round 6 – Bonuses Vary – ($.20) –  October 20, 2018  VISIT http://Vendicoins.com  Moderators: @Vendicoins & @Jercess
